reviewText: She may be young but want to start her out early.

I was very skeptical when I started watching this series but I've grown to really like it. Does it live up to the original movie? No, absolutely not. But I still enjoy it and I've even gotten a few laughs out of the show. The voice acting is very good and the animation is better in the second season. My only gripe is that it can be real cheesy at times but overall I like the show. Four stars.
Love The ADGTH movies and series and couldn't resist this set! Not disappointed and love to walk down memeory lane while watching. Hasn't gotten old, even after all these years!
